description.pr: Percurso circular com incio e fim em Almaceda. Segue emconjunto com o percurso verde de Almaceda, fazendo depoisligao a Martim Branco, Carvalheiras, Valbom e voltandoa ligar-se ao percurso verde at ao final em Almaceda.Acompanha a ribeira de Almaceda ao longo de grande partedo percurso. Percurso moderado.
description.en: Circular route starting and finishing at the MountainBiking Centre. At first, it coincides with the red route,before splitting off to the Serra da Pedragueira. It passesthrough the villages of Valbom and Martim Branco,then passes through Cho da V, Salgueiro do Campoand Palvarinho, finally rejoining the route that coincidesagain with the red route to Sarzedas. Difficult routewith a high degree of difficulty, only recommended forexperienced practitioners.
